=AIM_SKYRAMPS=

-----------------------------------

a simple aim map which balances the effectiveness of any weapon.....

Ideal for:
-Snipers
-Rifles
-Pistols
-Knives

The shadows and reflective water add an artistic feel to the level....

Optimized to run at over 100 fps with detailed water & very crisp shadows....

Give it a try with a few friends... i promise that you'll have fun.... XD
